roject_long_description','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">KCT is serving the needy since October 2012.. Our Concept is \"అన్నం పర భ్రహ్మ స్వరూపం\"  there are many needy and destitute people around us in this society. Many of them doesn\'t have proper food to feed themselves, Our Motto is Hungry Free Society. We have been serving at Rajahmundry, Visakhapatnam and Hyderabad, we also have volunteers from various locations in Andhra Pradesh and Telengana.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Concept of Hungry Van</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hungry Van is the van which we use to collect the food and distribute to the Orphanages, Old age Homes or Road side Street dwellers.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We Buy a Van (Tata Ace) our Volunteers use that van to collect the food and shift to other location.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>How It Works</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We receive calls from many people mentioning that they have left over food. The main question to us is the distance and the quality of food, our volunteers tests the quality of food but the transportation again becomes a big problem as the cooked food cannot be stored at one place for long time.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Benefits to Donor</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Any Corporate coming forward to invest in this project by sponsoring the vehicle is given facility of branding through our vehicle. Sides and Back Portion can be made with Signage of the Donors brand or business for 1 year. The Vehicle will be constantly roaming around to collect and distribute food and simultaneously the donor gets branding.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This facility is free for 1 year as the donor provides funding for the vehicle for 1 year, the whole of 1 year driver salary, maintenance, volunteers remuneration and diesel cost are adjusted from other donations.</p>\n'),(23,8,'ign_faqs','<p><strong>Is Karunya Charitable Trust Registered?</strong></p>\n<p>Yes. Reg. No. 85/2012</p>\n<p><strong>What are the Locations of Operation?</strong></p>\n<p>Vijayawada, Visakhapatnam, Rajahmundry and Hyderabad</p>\n<p><strong>Is this Organization Recognized by Government?</strong></p>\n<p>Yes. Karunya Charitable Trust (KCT) have been actively supporting government in various occasion like Pushkaras and during floods etc.</p>\n<p><strong>I have many doubts who can clarify?</strong></p>\n<p>You can call us on 7842200011</p>\n'),(24,8,'ign_product_level_count','1'),(25,8,'ign_option_project_url','current_page'),(26,8,'ign_fund_raised','0'),(27,8,'ign_percent_raised','0'),(28,8,'ign_days_left','0'),(29,8,'ign_project_closed',''),(30,8,'_edit_lock','1474376970:1'),(40,18,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(41,18,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(42,18,'_menu_item_object_id','2'),(43,18,'_menu_item_object','page'),(44,18,'_menu_item_target',''),(45,18,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(46,18,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(47,18,'_menu_item_url',''),(499,193,'testimonials-widget-company',''),(498,193,'testimonials-widget-location',''),(497,193,'testimonials-widget-title',''),(496,193,'testimonials-widget-author',''),(495,193,'_metaidlast','1'),(494,193,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_category',''),(493,193,'_edit_last','2'),(220,85,'_edit_lock','1529648196:1'),(219,85,'_wp_page_template','default'),(218,85,'_edit_last','2'),(94,2,'_edit_lock','1531132530:1'),(492,193,'_edit_lock','1523257157:2'),(491,185,'_ca_post_type','page'),(490,184,'_ca_post_type','page'),(489,182,'_edit_lock','1523130492:2'),(488,183,'_ca_post_type','page'),(487,181,'_seq_num','3'),(486,181,'_form_id','1'),(485,181,'_field_3','form submission test mail'),(484,181,'_field_6',''),(97,2,'_edit_last','1'),(568,222,'dismissable','1'),(115,36,'_wp_attached_file','2016/12/slide1.jpg'),(116,36,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:960;s:6:\"height\";i:720;s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"2016/12/slide1.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:8:{s