INSERT INTO `wpub_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2016-09-20 10:31:13','2016-09-20 10:31:13','Best SAP FICO Training Best SAP FICO Training in Hyderabad for better opportunity with our guidance and motivation. \r\n\r\n\r\n<em>SAP FICO</em> refers to the Finance (FI) &amp; Controlling (CO) is the Core modules of<em>SAP ERP</em> technique.\r\n<h2>Best SAP FICO Training</h2>\r\nThis is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:  Best SAP FICO Training\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://sapgtsonline.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!.\r\nSAP Controlling (CO) is another important SAP module offered to an organization. It supports coordination, monitoring, and optimization of all the processes in an organization. SAP CO includes managing and configuring master data that covers cost and profit centers, internal orders, and other cost elements and functional areas.\r\n<h1>First we will see what is FI and CO?</h1>\r\nSAP FI stands for Financial Accounting and it is one of important modules of SAP ERP. It is used to store the financial data of an organization. SAP FI helps <b>to analyze the financial conditions of a company in the market</b>. It can integrate with other SAP modules like SAP SD, SAP PP, SAP MM, SAP SCM, etc.\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para\"><b><i>SAP Introduction and Basics</i></b></p>\r\nBest SAP FICO  online training at IQ Online is a thorough course that is conducted online by industry veterans. The course covers all aspects of SAP FI and SAP CO module and equips individuals with the ability to better manage the financial accounting and reporting techniques for their organization.\r\n\r\nWe can say SAP FICO is an evergreen world of job creation and it has endless opportunities and you will have good job satisfaction. Suppose if have your company thoughts then better you work on it for few years in a big MNC company then come out and start your own firm, <b>become an Enterprenuer</b>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>How many phases does it contain?\r\nIt contains five phases:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Project preparation.</li>\r\n 	<li>EBusiness blue print</li>\r\n 	<li>Realization</li>\r\n 	<li>Final preparation</li>\r\n 	<li>Go live and support</li>\r\n</ul>','Sample Page','','publish','closed','open','','sample-page','','','2018-07-08 09:51:44','2018-07-08 09:51:44','',0,'http://sapgtsonline.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(7,1,'2016-09-20 11:58:04','2016-09-20 11:58:04','<label> Your Name (required)\r\n    [text* your-name] </label>\r\n\r\n<label> Email(required) [email* email-524] </label>\r\n\r\n<label> Your Contact No. (required)\r\n    [email* your-mobile] </label>\r\n<label> Qualification\r\n    [text your-subject] </label>\r\n\r\n<label> Your Message\r\n    [textarea your-message] </label>\r\n\r\n[submit \"Send\"]\n1\nInvest Start Up \"[your-subject]\"\n[your-name] <wordpress@sapgtsonline.com>\ngcrakesh.sapgts@gmail.com,kalyan.indian@gmail.com\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n[your-mobile]\r\n[email-524]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Invest Start Up (http://sapgtsonline.com)\nReply-To: me@example.com\n\n\n\n\nInvest Start Up 